To compile this software:

gcc -o client client.c
gcc -o server server.c

To run this software on the same machine:

Open two terminal windows.
Start the server in one terminal
and run the client from the other

To run the client try:

client 127.0.0.1 'Hello World!'

If you have the server running on a different machine then replace 127.0.0.1 
with the IP address of the other machine. 
